{
  "version": 15,
  "variables": [],
  "tiles": {
    "0": {
      "type": "markdown",
      "title": "",
      "content": "# 📡 [SNMP] Generic Device Dashboard\nDashboard genérico para monitoramento de dispositivos via SNMP. Ajuste os nomes das métricas conforme a nomenclatura do seu ambiente."
    },
    "1": {
      "type": "markdown",
      "title": "",
      "content": "## 🖥️ Device Details"
    },
    "2": {
      "type": "data",
      "title": "System Uptime by Device (days)",
      "query": "timeseries uptime = min(snmp.sysUpTimeInstance), by: {snmp_host}\n| fieldsAdd uptimeDays = uptime[] / 8640000",
      "davis": { "enabled": false, "davisVisualization": { "isAvailable": true } },
      "visualization": "lineChart",
      "visualizationSettings": {
        "thresholds": [],
        "chartSettings": { "gapPolicy": "connect", "circleChartSettings": { "groupingThresholdType": "relative", "groupingThresholdValue": 0, "valueType": "relative" }, "categoryOverrides": {} },
        "singleValue": { "showLabel": true, "label": "", "prefixIcon": "", "autoscale": true, "alignment": "center", "colorThresholdTarget": "value" },
        "table": { "rowDensity": "condensed", "enableSparklines": false, "hiddenColumns": [], "lineWrapIds": [], "columnWidths": {} },
        "honeycomb": { "shape": "hexagon", "legend": "auto", "dataMappings": {}, "displayedFields": [], "colorMode": "color-palette", "colorPalette": "categorical" },
        "histogram": { "dataMappings": [] }
      },
      "querySettings": { "maxResultRecords": 1000, "defaultScanLimitGbytes": 500, "maxResultMegaBytes": 1, "defaultSamplingRatio": 10, "enableSampling": false }
    },
    "3": {
      "type": "data",
      "title": "Device Interface Status — Admin vs Oper",
      "query": "timeseries adminStatus = max(snmp.ifAdminStatus), operStatus = max(snmp.ifOperStatus), by: {snmp_device, snmp_host}\n| fieldsAdd statusDiff = adminStatus[] - operStatus[]\n| fields timeframe, snmp_device, snmp_host, adminStatus, operStatus, statusDiff",
      "davis": { "enabled": false, "davisVisualization": { "isAvailable": true } },
      "visualization": "table",
      "visualizationSettings": {
        "thresholds": [],
        "chartSettings": { "gapPolicy": "connect", "circleChartSettings": { "groupingThresholdType": "relative", "groupingThresholdValue": 0, "valueType": "relative" }, "categoryOverrides": {} },
        "singleValue": { "showLabel": true, "label": "", "prefixIcon": "", "autoscale": true, "alignment": "center", "colorThresholdTarget": "value" },
        "table": { "rowDensity": "condensed", "enableSparklines": false, "hiddenColumns": [], "lineWrapIds": [], "columnWidths": {} },
        "honeycomb": { "shape": "hexagon", "legend": "auto", "dataMappings": {}, "displayedFields": [], "colorMode": "color-palette", "colorPalette": "categorical" },
        "histogram": { "dataMappings": [] }
      },
      "querySettings": { "maxResultRecords": 1000, "defaultScanLimitGbytes": 500, "maxResultMegaBytes": 1, "defaultSamplingRatio": 10, "enableSampling": false }
    },
    "4": {
      "type": "markdown",
      "title": "",
      "content": "## 🔌 Interfaces & Bandwidth\n\n**Inbound Util (%):** `(ifHCInOctets × 8 × 100) / (ifHighSpeed × 1.000.000)`\n\n**Outbound Util (%):** `(ifHCOutOctets × 8 × 100) / (ifHighSpeed × 1.000.000)`"
    },
    "5": {
      "type": "data",
      "title": "Device Interfaces — Speed e Octets In/Out",
      "query": "timeseries ifSpeed     = max(snmp.ifSpeed),\n            ifHighSpeed = max(snmp.ifHighSpeed),\n            octetsIn    = max(snmp.ifHCInOctets),\n            octetsOut   = max(snmp.ifHCOutOctets),\n            by: {snmp_host, interface}\n| fields timeframe, snmp_host, interface, ifSpeed, ifHighSpeed, octetsIn, octetsOut",
      "davis": { "enabled": false, "davisVisualization": { "isAvailable": true } },
      "visualization": "table",
      "visualizationSettings": {
        "thresholds": [],
        "chartSettings": { "gapPolicy": "connect", "circleChartSettings": { "groupingThresholdType": "relative", "groupingThresholdValue": 0, "valueType": "relative" }, "categoryOverrides": {} },
        "singleValue": { "showLabel": true, "label": "", "prefixIcon": "", "autoscale": true, "alignment": "center", "colorThresholdTarget": "value" },
        "table": { "rowDensity": "condensed", "enableSparklines": false, "hiddenColumns": [], "lineWrapIds": [], "columnWidths": {} },
        "honeycomb": { "shape": "hexagon", "legend": "auto", "dataMappings": {}, "displayedFields": [], "colorMode": "color-palette", "colorPalette": "categorical" },
        "histogram": { "dataMappings": [] }
      },
      "querySettings": { "maxResultRecords": 1000, "defaultScanLimitGbytes": 500, "maxResultMegaBytes": 1, "defaultSamplingRatio": 10, "enableSampling": false }
    },
    "6": {
      "type": "data",
      "title": "Inbound Bandwidth Utilization (%)",
      "query": "timeseries inOctets = avg(snmp.ifHCInOctets), highSpeed = avg(snmp.ifHighSpeed), by: {snmp_host, interface}\n| fieldsAdd inboundUtil = (inOctets[] * 8.0 * 100.0) / (highSpeed[] * 1000000.0)",
      "davis": { "enabled": false, "davisVisualization": { "isAvailable": true } },
      "visualization": "lineChart",
      "visualizationSettings": {
        "thresholds": [],
        "chartSettings": { "gapPolicy": "connect", "circleChartSettings": { "groupingThresholdType": "relative", "groupingThresholdValue": 0, "valueType": "relative" }, "categoryOverrides": {} },
        "singleValue": { "showLabel": true, "label": "", "prefixIcon": "", "autoscale": true, "alignment": "center", "colorThresholdTarget": "value" },
        "table": { "rowDensity": "condensed", "enableSparklines": false, "hiddenColumns": [], "lineWrapIds": [], "columnWidths": {} },
        "honeycomb": { "shape": "hexagon", "legend": "auto", "dataMappings": {}, "displayedFields": [], "colorMode": "color-palette", "colorPalette": "categorical" },
        "histogram": { "dataMappings": [] }
      },
      "querySettings": { "maxResultRecords": 1000, "defaultScanLimitGbytes": 500, "maxResultMegaBytes": 1, "defaultSamplingRatio": 10, "enableSampling": false }
    },
    "7": {
      "type": "data",
      "title": "Outbound Bandwidth Utilization (%)",
      "query": "timeseries outOctets = avg(snmp.ifHCOutOctets), highSpeed = avg(snmp.ifHighSpeed), by: {snmp_host, interface}\n| fieldsAdd outboundUtil = (outOctets[] * 8.0 * 100.0) / (highSpeed[] * 1000000.0)",
      "davis": { "enabled": false, "davisVisualization": { "isAvailable": true } },
      "visualization": "lineChart",
      "visualizationSettings": {
        "thresholds": [],
        "chartSettings": { "gapPolicy": "connect", "circleChartSettings": { "groupingThresholdType": "relative", "groupingThresholdValue": 0, "valueType": "relative" }, "categoryOverrides": {} },
